==Danish==
===Noun===
'''kønsord ''-en, ene'''''
#words that indicate or describe the [[genital]]s and therefor are often deemed offensive
#:''Du må ikke bruge '''kønsord''' i mormors hus.''
#:"You can't use explicit/foul/offensive language in grandma's house."

====Etymology====
Since the 1910s, from [[køn]] "sex, gender; genital(s)" and [[ord]] "word". Related to Swedish [[könsord]] with the same meaning.

